               <p>Bedouin-type dialect</p>
            </div>
            <div type="general">
               <p xml:space="preserve">Dahmani is located in the south western part of the governorate El Kef. While people can reach Dahmani and its surrounding area by shared mini buses, within the small town itself, the number of motorized vehicles seems relatively limited. Instead, locals use an athletic alternative riding on their bicycles, thus making up for the limitations of the local infrastructure.</p>
